---
description: Best practices for AWS SDK usage with boto3
globs: **/*.{py}
---
- Use resource abstractions for higher-level operations and easier code readability.
- Implement proper error handling with `try/except` blocks for AWS-specific exceptions.
- Use `boto3.client` for low-level operations and fine-grained control.
- Leverage `boto3.session.Session` for managing multiple AWS accounts or regions.
- Utilize `boto3.paginator` for handling paginated API responses efficiently.